OL,3,CNew Zealand PM apologises to 200,000
OL,4,Csurvivors of 'unimaginable' abuse
OL,6,FWatch Prime Minister Christopher Luxon
OL,7,Fmake his apology to survivors of abuse
OL,8,Fin New Zealand's parliament
OL,10,FNew Zealand's Prime Minister
OL,11,FChristopher Luxon has made a "formal
OL,12,Fand unreserved" apology for the
OL,13,F"unimaginable" abuse, torture and
OL,14,Fneglect of over 200,000 adults and
OL,15,Fchildren.
