OL,3,CNew Zealand PM apologises to 200,000
OL,4,Csurvivors of 'unimaginable' abuse
OL,6,FOf 650,000 vulnerable children and
OL,7,Fadults in the country's state, foster,
OL,8,Fand church care between 1950 and 2019,
OL,9,Fnearly a third endured physical,
OL,10,Fsexual, verbal or psychological abuse.
OL,11,FMany more were exploited or neglected.
OL,13,F"We will never know that true number,"
OL,14,FChris Hipkins, the leader of the
OL,15,Fopposition, told Parliament.
